longBusinessSummary: DLV Resources Ltd. does not have significant operations. The company intends to seek opportunities in the natural resource industry. Previously, it was operated in the mining sector. The company was formerly known as DV Resources Ltd. and changed its name to DLV Resources Ltd. in November 2017. DLV Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 1979 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
